    "patch_code": "public static String parseName(byte[] buffer, final int offset, final int length) {\n    StringBuilder result = new StringBuilder(length);\n    int end = offset + length;\n    \n    for (int i = offset; i < end; ++i) {\n        if (buffer[i] == 0) {\n            break;\n        }\n        \n        if ((buffer[i] & 0x80) != 0) {\n            // UTF-8 BOM signature detected\n            ++i;\n            continue;\n        } else if ((buffer[i] & 0xFF) > 127) {\n            // Non-ASCII character\n            byte b1 = 0;\n            if (i + 1 < end && (buffer[i+1] & 0xC0) == 0x80) {\n                b1 = buffer[i+1];\n                ++i;\n            }\n            \n            result.append(String.format(\"%c%c\", buffer[i], b1));\n            continue;\n        }\n        \n        result.append((char) buffer[i]);\n    }\n\n    return result.toString();\n}",
    "patch_status": "TRIGGER_ERROR",
